---

<BaseLayout>
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 align-text-top">Our Family</h1>
  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold ml-2">Convenor</h2>
  <div class="flex items-start mb-8">
    <div class="w-80 rounded-full mr-4">
      <img
        src="/profile.jpeg"
        alt="Dr. Ankur Gupta"
        class="w-full h-full rounded-full object-cover"
      />
    </div>

    <div>
      <div class="space-y-0.1">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">Dr. Ankur Gupta</h2>
      </div>
      <p>
        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Ab ea officiis,
        suscipit totam iusto, excepturi dolor consequatur, cumque nam veniam
        impedit quia libero fugiat! Nobis, vel consequuntur! Doloribus pariatur
        quia iste rem cumque accusantium ducimus adipisci expedita natus rerum
        fugiat quos exercitationem, odit saepe veniam omnis deserunt quaerat
        consectetur dolores!
      </p>
      <h3 class="font-bold">Email</h3>
      <p>abc@gmail.com</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Current Members</h2>

  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-10">
    <!-- Row 1 -->
    <div class="flex flex-col">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">PhD</h3>
      <div class="flex items-start bg-white shadow-md rounded-lg p-4 mb-4">
        <div class="w-48 rounded-full overflow-hidden mr-4">
          <img
            src="/profile.jpeg"
            alt="Mohd. Imran"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
          />
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="text-xl font-medium">Mohd. Imran</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-600">PhD</p>
          <p class="mt-2">
            Research on machine learning applications in healthcare. Passionate
            about AI and its impact on society.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-start bg-white shadow-md rounded-lg p-4">
        <div class="w-48 rounded-full overflow-hidden mr-4">
          <img
            src="/profile.jpeg"
            alt="Jane Doe"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
          />
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="text-xl font-medium">Jane Doe</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-600">PhD</p>
          <p class="mt-2">
            Focused on natural language processing and its applications in
            education. Enthusiastic about data science.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-col">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">M.Tech</h3>
      <div class="flex items-start bg-white shadow-md rounded-lg p-4 mb-4">
        <div class="w-48 h-24 rounded-full overflow-hidden mr-4">
          <img
            src="/profile.jpeg"
            alt="MTech Student"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
          />
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="text-xl font-medium">Ali Khan</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-600">MTech</p>
          <p class="mt-2">
            Specializing in cybersecurity and network protocols. Interested in
            ethical hacking and information security.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-start bg-white shadow-md rounded-lg p-4">
        <div class="w-48 rounded-full overflow-hidden mr-4">
          <img
            src="/profile.jpeg"
            alt="Sara Lee"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
          />
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="text-xl font-medium">Sara Lee</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-600">MTech</p>
          <p class="mt-2">
            Focused on data analytics and visualization. Loves working with big
            data and creating insightful reports.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Row 2 -->
    <div class="flex flex-col">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Research Assistants</h3>
      <div class="flex items-start bg-white shadow-md rounded-lg p-4 mb-4">
        <div class="w-48 rounded-full overflow-hidden mr-4">
          <img
            src="/profile.jpeg"
            alt="Assistant Name"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
          />
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="text-xl font-medium">John Smith</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Assistant</p>
          <p class="mt-2">
            Provides administrative support and assists in research projects.
            Enjoys problem-solving and team collaboration.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-start bg-white shadow-md rounded-lg p-4">
        <div class="w-48 rounded-full overflow-hidden mr-4">
          <img
            src="/profile.jpeg"
            alt="Emily White"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
          />
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="text-xl font-medium">Emily White</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Assistant</p>
          <p class="mt-2">
            Expert in project management and communication. Passionate about
            helping teams achieve their goals.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-col">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Interns</h3>
      <div class="flex items-start bg-white shadow-md rounded-lg p-4 mb-4">
        <div class="w-48 rounded-full overflow-hidden mr-4">
          <img
            src="/profile.jpeg"
            alt="Intern Name"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
          />
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="text-xl font-medium">Michael Brown</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Intern</p>
          <p class="mt-2">
            Currently exploring AI and machine learning technologies. Eager to
            learn and contribute to innovative projects.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-start bg-white shadow-md rounded-lg p-4">
        <div class="w-48 rounded-full overflow-hidden mr-4">
          <img
            src="/profile.jpeg"
            alt="Laura Green"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
          />
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="text-xl font-medium">Laura Green</h4>
